<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA611_04_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema611_04.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema611_04_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
          <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
            <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
              <div class="fraction_box ml_0">
                <span>2</span>
                <span>3</span>
              </div>
              ÷5를 어떻게 계산하는지 알아봅시다.
            </div>
          </div>
        </h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">
            <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
              <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                <span class="fraction_box ml_0">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
                ÷5를 어떻게 계산할 수 있을지 이야기해 보세요.
              </div>
            </div>
          </h3>

          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">분자 2가 자연수 5로 나누어떨어지도록 크기가 같은 분수로 바꾸어 계산합니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">
            <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
              <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                그림을 이용하여
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
                ÷5를 계산하는 방법을 알아보세요.
              </div>
            </div>
          </h3>

          <div class="question_box">
            <div class="left_box">
              <div class="left_top_box">
                <div class="text_box">
                  <div class="flex ">
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span>3</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>2×5</span>
                      <span>3×5</span>
                    </span>
                    <span>=</span>
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>10</span>
                      <span>15</span>
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="img_box">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0004_block1.svg" alt="">
                  <span>=</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0004_block2.svg" alt="">
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="left_btm_box">
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  <span>분자가 5로 나누어떨어지도록</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>3</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>와 크기가</span>
                </div>
                <span>같은 분수를 만들어요.</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0004_arrow.svg" alt="">
            <div class="mid_box">
              <div class="mid_top_box">
                <div class="text_box">
                  <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>2</span>
                      <span>3</span>
                    </span>
                    <span>÷5</span>
                  </div>
                  <span>=</span>
                  <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                    <span class="fraction_box">
                      <span>10</span>
                      <span>15</span>
                    </span>
                    <span>÷5</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="img_box">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0004_block3.svg" alt="">
                  <span>=</span>
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA611_04_SU/0004_block4.svg" alt="">
                </div>
              
                <div class="bg"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="mid_btm_box">
                <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                  <span class="fraction_box">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>3</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>÷5 의 몫과</span>
                  <span class="fraction_box m_rl">
                    <span>2</span>
                    <span>3</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>÷10 의 몫은 서로 같아요.</span>
                </div>
              
                <div class="bg"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="right_box">
              <div class="flex align_center gap_4">
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>2</span>
                  <span>3</span>
                </span>
                <span>÷5=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap up">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="10" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                  </span>
                  <span>15</span>
                </span>
                <span>÷5=</span>
                <span class="fraction_box">
                  <span>
                    <div class="input_wrap up">
                      <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="10" text-align="center"></math-field>
                    </div>
                    <span>÷5</span>
                  </span>
                  <span>15</span>
                </span>
                <span>=</span>
                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                  <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(15)" text-align="center"></math-field>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_3"> 
          <h3 lang="y">(분수)÷(자연수)를 계산하는 방법을 이야기해 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="input_area">
            <div class="input_wrap">
              <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
              <div class="example_box">
                <p lang="y">
                  분자가 자연수의 배수인 경우에는 분자를 자연수로 나누어 계산하고, 분자가 자연수의 배수가 아닌 경우에는 크기가 같은 분수 중에서 분자가 자연수의 배수인 분수로 바꾸어 계산합니다.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
          <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
